_sText:
THIS MAP PACK CONTAINS 2 ZOMBIE MOD MAPS


Contents:
This map pack contains 2 maps for zombie mod. The first being "Zm Lila Panic Redemptionv3 fix", which is a fixed version that focuses on visual and gameplay tweaks. The second map is "Zm FireWaLL Flats Fix", in which takes place in a small office complex with many places to camp and hide from the zombies. There are multiple levels to this map with secrets beyond the walls.

Support:
Optimization, 64 Player Support, Custom textures, secret areas
